āi","e":"the sky","i":"السَّمَآءِ"},{"b":"6.7","h":"9.12","c":"فَوۡقَهُمۡ","d":"fawqahum","e":"above them","i":"فَوۡقَهُمۡ"},{"b":"7.9","h":"10.92","c":"كَيۡفَ","d":"kayfa","e":"how","i":"كَيۡفَ"},{"b":"8.6","h":"12.01","c":"بَنَيۡنَٰهَا","d":"banaynāhā","e":"We structured it","i":"بَنَيۡنٰهَا"},{"b":"10.1","h":"14.69","c":"وَزَيَّنَّـٰهَا","d":"wazayyannāhā","e":"and adorned it","i":"وَزَ يَّـنّٰهَا"},{"b":"12.","h":"18.35","c":"وَمَا","d":"wamā","e":"and not","i":"وَمَا"},{"b":"13.6","h":"19.48","c":"لَهَا","d":"lahā","e":"for it","i":"لَهَا"},{"b":"14.3","h":"20.62","c":"مِن","d":"min","e":"any","i":"مِنۡ"},{"b":"15.4","h":"21.64","c":"فُرُوجٖ","d":"furūjin","e":"rifts","i":"فُرُوۡجٍ"}],"a":{"g":"Have they not looked at the heaven above them - how We structured it and adorned it and [how] it has no rifts?"}},"7":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.75","c":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضَ","d":"wal-arḍa","e":"And the earth","i":"وَالۡاَرۡضَ"},{"b":"1.1","h":"2.19","c":"مَدَدۡنَٰهَا","d":"madadnāhā","e":"We have spread it out","i":"مَدَدۡنٰهَا"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.82","c":"وَأَلۡقَيۡنَا","d":"wa-alqaynā","e":"and cast","i":"وَاَ لۡقَيۡنَا"},{"b":"4.2","h":"7.26","c":"فِيهَا","d":"fīhā","e":"therein","i":"فِيۡهَا"},{"b":"5.1","h":"8.72","c":"رَوَٰسِيَ","d":"rawāsiya","e":"firmly set mountains","i":"رَوَاسِىَ"},{"b":"6.4","h":"10.85","c":"وَأَنۢبَتۡنَا","d":"wa-anbatnā","e":"and We made to grow","i":"وَاَنۡۢبَتۡنَا"},{"b":"8.6","h":"13.66","c":"فِيهَا","d":"fīhā","e":"therein","i":"فِيۡهَا"},{"b":"9.6","h":"15.44","c":"مِن","d":"min","e":"of","i":"مِنۡ"},{"b":"10.7","h":"16.39","c":"كُلِّ","d":"kulli","e":"every","i":"كُلِّ"},{"b":"11.4","h":"17.42","c":"زَوۡجِۭ","d":"zawjin","e":"kind","i":"زَوۡجٍۢ"},{"b":"13.","h":"19.48","c":"بَهِيجٖ","d":"bahījin","e":"beautiful","i":"بَهِيۡجٍۙ"}],"a":{"g":"And the earth - We spread it out and cast therein firmly set mountains and made grow therein [something] of every beautiful kind,"}},"8":{"w":[{"b":"0.11","h":"1.35","c":"تَبۡصِرَةٗ","d":"tabṣiratan","e":"G