","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"in","i":"فِىۡ"},{"b":"2.5","h":"3.09","c":"ذَٰلِكَ","d":"dhālika","e":"that","i":"ذٰلِكَ"},{"b":"3.6","h":"4.54","c":"لَذِكۡرَىٰ","d":"ladhik'rā","e":"surely, is a reminder","i":"لَذِكۡرٰى"},{"b":"4.7","h":"6.31","c":"لِمَن","d":"liman","e":"for (one) who","i":"لِمَنۡ"},{"b":"6.0","h":"7.75","c":"كَانَ","d":"kāna","e":"is","i":"كَانَ"},{"b":"6.8","h":"8.92","c":"لَهُۥ","d":"lahu","e":"for him","i":"لَهٗ"},{"b":"7.6","h":"9.96","c":"قَلۡبٌ","d":"qalbun","e":"a heart","i":"قَلۡبٌ"},{"b":"8.5","h":"11.42","c":"أَوۡ","d":"aw","e":"or","i":"اَوۡ"},{"b":"9.0","h":"12.1","c":"أَلۡقَى","d":"alqā","e":"(who) gives ear","i":"اَلۡقَى"},{"b":"9.6","h":"13.19","c":"ٱلسَّمۡعَ","d":"l-samʿa","e":"(who) gives ear","i":"السَّمۡعَ"},{"b":"10.6","h":"14.68","c":"وَهُوَ","d":"wahuwa","e":"while he","i":"وَهُوَ"},{"b":"11.3","h":"15.76","c":"شَهِيدٞ","d":"shahīdun","e":"(is) a witness","i":"شَهِيۡدٌ"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed in that is a reminder for whoever has a heart or who listens while he is present [in mind]."}},"38":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.4","c":"وَلَقَدۡ","d":"walaqad","e":"And certainly","i":"وَلَقَدۡ"},{"b":"0.89","h":"1.39","c":"خَلَقۡنَا","d":"khalaqnā","e":"We created","i":"خَلَقۡنَا"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.76","c":"ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ","d":"l-samāwāti","e":"the heavens","i":"السَّمٰوٰتِ"},{"b":"3.6","h":"5.28","c":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضَ","d":"wal-arḍa","e":"and the earth","i":"وَالۡاَرۡضَ"},{"b":"4.8","h":"6.98","c":"وَمَا","d":"wamā","e":"and whatever","i":"وَمَا"},{"b":"5.5","h":"8.05","c":"بَيۡنَهُمَا","d":"baynahumā","e":"(is) between both of them","i":"بَيۡنَهُمَا"},{"b":"6.9","h":"10.02","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"in","i":"فِىۡ"},{"b":"7.4","h":"10.83","c":"سِتَّةِ","d":"sittati","e":"six","i":"سِتَّةِ"},{"b":"8.4","h":"12.22","c":"أَيَّامٖ","d":"ayyāmin","e":"periods","i":"اَيَّامٍۖ"},{"b":"10.5","h":"14.8","c":"وَمَا","d":"wamā","e":"and (did) not","i":"وَّمَا"},{"b":"11.2","h":"15.91","c":"مَسَّنَا","d":"massanā","e":"touch Us","i":"مَسَّنَا"},{"b":"12.4","h":"17.71","c":"مِن","d":"min","e":"any","i":"مِنۡ"},{"b":"12.6","h":"18.04","c":"لُّغُوبٖ","d":"lughūbin","e":"fatigue","i":"لُّغُوۡبٍ"}],"a":{"g":"And We did certainly create the heavens and earth and what is between them in six days, and there touched Us no weariness."}},"39":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.75","c":"فَٱصۡبِرۡ","d":"fa-iṣ'bir","e":"So be patient","i":"فَاصۡبِرۡ"},{"b":"0.84","h":"1.84","c":"عَلَىٰ","d":"ʿalā","e":"over","i":"عَلٰى"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.09","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"what","i":"مَا"},{"b":"2.0","h":"3.88","c":"يَقُولُونَ","d":"yaqūlūna","e":"they say","i":"يَقُوۡلُوۡنَ"},{"b":"3.5","h":"6.21","c":"وَسَبِّحۡ","d":"wasabbiḥ","e":"and glorify","i":"وَسَبِّحۡ"},{"b":"4.7","h":"7.82","c":"بِحَمۡدِ","d":"biḥamdi","e":"(the) praise","i":"بِحَمۡدِ"},{"b":"5.6","h":"9.34","c":"رَبِّكَ","d":"rabbika","e":"(of) your Lord","i":"رَبِّكَ"},{"b":"6.6","h":"10.84","c":"قَبۡلَ","d":"qabla","e":"before","i":"قَبۡلَ"},{"b":"7.3","h":"11.85","c":"طُلُوعِ","d":"ṭulūʿi","e":"(the) rising","i":"طُلُوۡعِ"},{"b":"8.2","h":"13.37","c":"ٱلشَّمۡسِ","d":"l-shamsi","e":"(of) the sun","i":"الشَّمۡسِ"},{"b":"9.2","h":"14.87","c":"وَقَبۡلَ","d":"waqabla","e":"and before","i":"وَقَبۡلَ"},{"b":"10.1","h":"16.33","c":"ٱلۡغُرُوبِ","d":"l-ghurūbi","e":"the setting","i":"الۡغُرُوۡبِۚ"}],"a":{"g":"So be patient, [O Muhammad], over what they say and exalt [Allah] with praise of your Lord before the rising of the sun and before its setting,"}},"40":{"w":[{"b":"0.07","h":"0.45","c":"وَمِنَ","d":"wamina","e":"And of","i":"وَمِنَ"},{"b":"0.72","h":"1.19","c":"ٱلَّيۡلِ","d":"al-layli","e":"the night","i":"الَّيۡلِ"},{"b":"1.6","h":"2.52","c":"فَسَبِّحۡهُ","d":"fasabbiḥ'hu","e":"glorify Him","i":"فَسَبِّحۡهُ"},{"b":"3.1","h":"4.69","c":"وَأَدۡبَٰرَ","d":"wa-adbāra","e":"and after","i":"وَاَدۡبَارَ"},{"b":"4.4","h":"6.84","c":"ٱلسُّجُودِ","d":"l-sujūdi","e":"the prostration","i":"السُّجُوۡدِ"}],"a":{"g":"And [in part] of the night exalt Him and after prostration."}},"41":{"w":[{"b":"0.07","h":"0.7