on"}},"44":{"w":[{"b":"0.08","h":"0.7","c":"يَوۡمَ","d":"yawma","e":"(The) Day","i":"يَوۡمَ"},{"b":"0.64","h":"1.59","c":"تَشَقَّقُ","d":"tashaqqaqu","e":"will split","i":"تَشَقَّقُ"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.52","c":"ٱلۡأَرۡضُ","d":"l-arḍu","e":"the earth","i":"الۡاَرۡضُ"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.76","c":"عَنۡهُمۡ","d":"ʿanhum","e":"from them","i":"عَنۡهُمۡ"},{"b":"3.6","h":"6.19","c":"سِرَاعٗاۚ","d":"sirāʿan","e":"hurrying","i":"سِرَاعًاؕ"},{"b":"5.3","h":"9.75","c":"ذَٰلِكَ","d":"dhālika","e":"That","i":"ذٰ لِكَ"},{"b":"6.2","h":"10.9","c":"حَشۡرٌ","d":"ḥashrun","e":"(is) a gathering","i":"حَشۡرٌ"},{"b":"7.2","h":"12.3","c":"عَلَيۡنَا","d":"ʿalaynā","e":"for Us","i":"عَلَيۡنَا"},{"b":"8.4","h":"14.64","c":"يَسِيرٞ","d":"yasīrun","e":"easy","i":"يَسِيۡرٌ"}],"a":{"g":"On the Day the earth breaks away from them [and they emerge] rapidly; that is a gathering easy for Us."}},"45":{"w":[{"b":"0.05","h":"0.15","c":"نَّحۡنُ","d":"naḥnu","e":"We","i":"نَحۡنُ"},{"b":"0.7","h":"0.99","c":"أَعۡلَمُ","d":"aʿlamu","e":"know best","i":"اَعۡلَمُ"},{"b":"1.6","h":"2.32","c":"بِمَا","d":"bimā","e":"[of] what","i":"بِمَا"},{"b":"2.2","h":"3.38","c":"يَقُولُونَۖ","d":"yaqūlūna","e":"they say","i":"يَقُوۡلُوۡنَ​"},{"b":"5.7","h":"5.73","c":"وَمَآ","d":"wamā","e":"and not","i":"وَمَاۤ"},{"b":"8.0","h":"6.34","c":"أَنتَ","d":"anta","e":"(are) you","i":"اَنۡتَ"},{"b":"9.2","h":"9.34","c":"عَلَيۡهِم","d":"ʿalayhim","e":"over them","i":"عَلَيۡهِمۡ"},{"b":"11.4","h":"11.75","c":"بِجَبَّارٖۖ","d":"bijabbārin","e":"the one to compel","i":"بِجَـبَّارٍ​"},{"b":"15.6","h":"16.85","c":"فَذَكِّرۡ","d":"fadhakkir","e":"But remind","i":"فَذَكِّرۡ"},{"b":"16.7","h":"18.42","c":"بِٱلۡقُرۡءَانِ","d":"bil-qur'āni","e":"with the Quran","i":"بِالۡقُرۡاٰنِ"},{"b":"18.6","h":"20.93","c":"مَن","d":"man","e":"whoever","i":"مَنۡ"},{"b":"19.8","h":"22.29","c":"يَخَافُ","d":"yakhāfu","e":"fears","i":"يَّخَافُ"},{"b":"20.9","h":"23.79","c":"وَعِيدِ","d":"waʿīdi","e":"My threat","i":"وَعِيۡدِ"}],"a":{"g":"We are most knowing of what they say, and you are not over them a tyrant. But remind by the Qur'an whoever fears My threat."}}}